Training pipeline for encoder -> TPSAPU backbone -> decoder experiments.
Default schedule: 5 warmup epochs 35 cosine-annealing training epochs 20
L2-pruning epochs on the TPSAPU shared recurrent topology Example: python
train_pipeline.py --encoder linear_patch --decoder membrane_mlp

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --dataset {mnist,cifar10,imagenet,tiny_imagenet}
  --data-dir DATA_DIR
  --backbone {tpsapu,tpsapu_per_tau,tpsapu_cross_reservoir,tpsapu_per_tau_cross_reservoir}
                        tpsapu shares recurrent topology across tau
                        reservoirs; tpsapu_per_tau gives each tau its own
                        recurrent matrix while keeping the input projection
                        shared; tpsapu_cross_reservoir adds compressed
                        communication between tau reservoirs;
                        tpsapu_per_tau_cross_reservoir combines per-tau
                        recurrent matrices with compressed communication.
  --encoder {linear_patch,mlp_patch,lif_2x2,cnn2,cnn3,res_cnn,patch,rows}
  --decoder {linear,membrane_mlp,spike_mlp,both_mlp,all_state_mlp,membrane_transformer,spike_transformer,both_transformer,all_state_transformer,lif_count,mlp}
  --pooling {last,mean}
  --image-size IMAGE_SIZE
  --in-channels IN_CHANNELS
  --num-classes NUM_CLASSES
  --embed-dim EMBED_DIM
  --reservoir-dim RESERVOIR_DIM
  --taus TAUS
  --input-hidden-dim INPUT_HIDDEN_DIM
  --cross-rank CROSS_RANK
                        Low-rank channel count for cross-reservoir backbone
                        variants.
  --cross-gain CROSS_GAIN
                        Scale for cross-reservoir current; used by cross-
                        reservoir variants.
  --patch-size PATCH_SIZE
  --encoder-hidden-dim ENCODER_HIDDEN_DIM
  --cnn-channels CNN_CHANNELS
  --lif-white-threshold LIF_WHITE_THRESHOLD
  --encoder-dropout ENCODER_DROPOUT
  --decoder-hidden-dim DECODER_HIDDEN_DIM
  --decoder-dropout DECODER_DROPOUT
  --decoder-transformer-layers DECODER_TRANSFORMER_LAYERS
  --decoder-transformer-heads DECODER_TRANSFORMER_HEADS
  --decoder-transformer-ff-mult DECODER_TRANSFORMER_FF_MULT
  --decoder-max-steps DECODER_MAX_STEPS
  --recurrent-drop RECURRENT_DROP
  --warmup-epochs WARMUP_EPOCHS
  --cosine-epochs COSINE_EPOCHS
  --cosine-cycles COSINE_CYCLES
                        Number of cosine annealing descents; 1.0 decays once
                        from base LR to min LR.
  --prune-epochs PRUNE_EPOCHS
  --prune-cycles PRUNE_CYCLES
                        Number of pruning-phase cosine annealing descents.
  --min-lr-ratio MIN_LR_RATIO
  --prune-lr-scale PRUNE_LR_SCALE
  --l2-prune-start-lambda L2_PRUNE_START_LAMBDA
  --l2-prune-growth-epochs L2_PRUNE_GROWTH_EPOCHS
  --prune-threshold PRUNE_THRESHOLD
  --target-sparsity TARGET_SPARSITY
  --prune-start-sparsity PRUNE_START_SPARSITY
  --prune-ramp-epochs PRUNE_RAMP_EPOCHS
  --prune-stabilize-epochs PRUNE_STABILIZE_EPOCHS
  --keep-dropout-during-prune
  --neuron-prune
  --neuron-prune-target-sparsity NEURON_PRUNE_TARGET_SPARSITY
  --neuron-spike-threshold NEURON_SPIKE_THRESHOLD
  --neuron-membrane-std-threshold NEURON_MEMBRANE_STD_THRESHOLD
  --neuron-prune-min-keep NEURON_PRUNE_MIN_KEEP
  --batch-size BATCH_SIZE
  --lr LR
  --weight-decay WEIGHT_DECAY
  --grad-clip GRAD_CLIP
  --num-workers NUM_WORKERS
                        DataLoader worker processes. Default 0 keeps dataset
                        decoding in the main process and avoids hidden worker-
                        subprocess crashes.
  --log-batches LOG_BATCHES
                        Print running loss/accuracy every N batches; disabled
                        by default.
  --train-samples TRAIN_SAMPLES
  --test-samples TEST_SAMPLES
  --validation-source {dataset,train_split}
                        Use the dataset validation/test split for per-epoch
                        validation, or hold out part of the training split and
                        reserve the dataset validation/test split for final
                        testing.
  --train-val-fraction TRAIN_VAL_FRACTION
                        Fraction of the training split to hold out when
                        --validation-source=train_split.
  --train-val-samples TRAIN_VAL_SAMPLES
                        Fixed training-split validation size; overrides
                        --train-val-fraction when positive.
  --eval-test-after-training
                        Evaluate the reserved dataset validation/test split
                        once after training completes.
  --continuous, --no-continuous
                        Keep training indefinitely. Warmup/cosine runs until
                        the pruning stage is reached; pruning then repeats
                        LR/L2 cycles while keeping the pruning mask. Without
                        pruning, cosine cycles repeat forever.
  --seed SEED
  --no-download         Use only already-cached datasets; fail fast instead of
                        contacting remote hosts.
  --download            Allow dataset downloads when an entry point defaults
                        to --no-download.
  --checkpoint-out CHECKPOINT_OUT
  --log-dir LOG_DIR
  --resume RESUME
